  "text": "Once the MD simulations were analyzed, we proceeded to compare the EDA of the generated trajectories with the reference modes obtained from the crystal structures. A previous report benchmarked the sampling of MD protein simulations against ANM and PCA using 20 ns trajectories. [CITATION_1] Those authors concluded that generating conformers using the softest ANM modes covered a more comprehensive subspace than the MD ensembles. Moreover, ANM requires very low computational resources compared to conventional methods.",
